Ivan Simon Cary Elwes -LRB- -LSB- ˈɛlwɪs -RSB- born 26 October 1962 -RRB- , known professionally as Cary Elwes , is an English actor and writer .
He is best known for his roles in films such as The Princess Bride , Glory , Robin Hood : Men in Tights , Days of Thunder , Bram Stoker 's Dracula , Hot Shots !
, Twister , The Jungle Book , Liar , Liar , and Saw .
He has also had recurring roles in series such as The X-Files and Psych , and currently stars in the Crackle series The Art of More .